{"word":"ἀνακομίζω","slug":"ἀνακομίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνακομίζω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to carry up</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be carried up stream</i>, or <i>up the country</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to bring back, recover</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: —<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> (with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a>) <i>to take back with one</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be brought back</i>, and of persons, <i>to return</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> also, <i>to bring to pass</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>:— <i>to bring back upon oneself</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}